assessment
Please follow below instruction to get the project runing on your local machine. For any question or issues experianced, please email: eugene.maboe@gmail.com

System prerequisite

java 1.8 or higher.

Gradle 5.0 or highter (But gradle wrapper in project should work)

clone project from github.

open terminal on project root.

enter command, gradle clean build (To download all project dependencies)

enter command gradle bootRun to run project.

Once project is running, please goto http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html# for api documentation. username: user password: password

To hit program api endpoint: http://localhost:8080/getWeather For Authorization username: user password: password